<p><em>Read about the talk that stole the show at a recent ME/CFS conference in <strong>Simon McGrath&#8217;s</strong> two-part blog. Here&#8217;s Part 1 &#8230;<br />
</em></p>
<div id="attachment_27884" style="width: 195px" class="wp-caption alignright"><a href="http://blog.wellcome.ac.uk/2011/08/22/george-davey-smith/" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-27884" src="http://phoenixrising.me/wp-content/uploads/DaveySmith1.jpg" alt="George Davey Smith" width="185" height="135" /></a>
